Just to touch on a few things i saw.  <br>
Resists vs hp.  <br>
<br>
Once you have 200 in the resist you are looking for any more is effectively pointless.  Considering buffs and base resists there is only a relatively small amount of +resist you need at any one given time.<br>
<br>
HP never loose their marginal gain.  Therefore HP &gt; resists ASSUMING you have a baseline resist lvl.  Hell, later in the game you run into mobs with lure based ae where resist gear is pointless.<br>
<br>
That said perhaps hp should be weighted more than resists.<br>
<br>
