From the various reading material I have read for both casters and for melees the conclusive material shows that stats in EQ really do not mean much, unless in large quantities.<br>
<br>
For example, 5str will not make a difference in a melee's damage output, but 80str will add a little (not enuff to warrent adding more STR for damage output).<br>
